title: Fautor lepton
content:
Fautor lepton is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk, in the family Calliostomatidae within the superfamily Trochoidea, the top snails, turban snails and their allies.[1]

The length of the shell attains 12.6 mm.

This marine species occurs off Tuamotu.
